node.text:
I spent a day with @coralrestorationfoundation learning about coral reefs and their fight to survive. I didn’t realize how badly reefs need our help! The reefs in the Keys, the ones I grew up swimming in and fishing on, are disappearing.
But the team at Coral Restoration Foundation made me hopeful. They are using science to restore and rebuild coral reefs! I went diving in their giant open ocean coral nurseries where they raise corals! Then we gathered some of those nursery raised corals and returned them to the wild coral reef nearby! The work they are doing everyday was so inspiring and I’m so happy to have been a part of it!
